<paragraph blockId="28.[151,1437,1772,2013]" box="[151,1399,1772,1797]" pageId="28" pageNumber="529">Syntypes, sex and number not stated, lost; formerly in Dejean Collection, but now not in OUMNH or MNHNP.</paragraph>
